LerretFixtureMono — provenance and license
==========================================

LerretFixtureMono.woff2 was authored from scratch for the Lerret project by
the Lerret authors. It copies no existing typeface and carries no third-party
copyright. Every glyph is a solid full-em rectangle — a deliberately simple
shape that proves, by eye, that a font dropped into `.lerret/_fonts/` is
auto-registered and available to assets by family name with no manual
`@font-face` declarations needed.

